<plot>A family mourns about the death of their daughter, each in a very different way. One day, a young girl appears at their doorsteps, injured, confused, and without any memory. She completely experiences the world anew, without any judgment and conditioning of the past. By taking care of the young girl, the family's pain transforms until an unexpected event stirs up secrets from the past.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?619777</url></doc>
